uz sentinel netflix ceo gives  million to open charter schools by matt king july    a b washington post netflix’s reed hastings has a big idea kill elected school boards by valerie strauss march    response to netflix ceo reed hastings  alturrick kenney and bob peterson the real news network   a b technology network  new york times one mans  challenges by laurie j flynn june    wall street journal expense it april    los angeles times state gop awash in red ink by evan halper august    california secretary of state  calaccess  campaign finance calaccesssoscagov retrieved june      archived april   at the wayback machine  a b wall street journal netflixs ceo is mobilizing for battle with amazon by carl bialik october    the next web article external linksedit reed hastings at microsoftcom reed hastings biography at netflixcom reed hastings articles on peace corps online reed hastings interview on national public radio part of business s list of  people who dont matter part of times  most influential people v t e microsoft history all topics people list founders bill gates paul allen board of directors john w thompson chairman satya nadella ceo dina dublon maria klawe david marquardt charles noski helmut panke mason morfit john w stanton senior leadership team satya nadella ceo scott guthrie amy hood cfo terry myerson harry shum corporate vps gabe aul vp joe belfiore richard rashid svp s somasegar svp divisions engineering groups mobile skype unit digital crimes unit garage press research studios net foundation outercurve foundation estates microsoft redmond campus microsoft talo microsoft algeria microsoft egypt microsoft india microsoft japan product families operating systems windows software office servers visual studio hardware hololens surface xbox web properties bing channel  codeplex developer network msn mixer officecom onedrive outlookcom technet windows store conferences build mix pdc teched winhec inspire criticism bundling of microsoft windows clippy iloo