oud networking services since july  and serves on its audit committee ms mather has also been an independent trustee to the dodge  cox funds board of trustees since may  ms mather was previously a director of central european media enterprises group a developer and operator of national commercial television channels and stations in central and eastern europe from  to  zapposcom inc a privately held online retailer until it was acquired by amazoncom inc in  ariat international inc a privatelyheld manufacturer of footwear for equestrian athletes from  to  and moneygram international inc a global payment services company from may  to may  and solazyme inc a renewable oil and bioproducts company from april  to november  from  to  ms mather was executive vice president and chief financial officer of pixar a computer animation studio prior to her service at pixar ms mather was executive vice president and chief financial officer of village roadshow pictures the film production division of village roadshow limited from  to  she held various executive positions at the walt disney company including senior vice president of finance and administration for its buena vista international theatrical division ms mather was made an honorary fellow of sidney sussex college cambridge in october  chairman of the audit committee brad smith president and chief legal officer microsoft corp brad smith has served as one of the companys directors since march  in his role at microsoft smith plays a key role in representing the company externally and in leading the companys work on a number of critical issues including privacy security accessibility environmental sustainability and digital inclusion among others mr smith joined microsoft in  and became general counsel in  he spent three years leading the companys legal and corporate affairs team in europe and five years as deputy general counsel responsible for such teams outside the us his area of expertise includes competition law intellectu